  "description": {
    "S": "Hearty and healthy, this Turkey Sweet Potato Chili is packed with tender sweet potatoes, ground turkey, beans, and warm spices. A squeeze of lime at the end brightens everything up. Perfect for weeknight dinners or meal prep, and topped with your favorites like cheese, Greek yogurt, or avocado."
  },
